Upload any design in seconds and receive a detailed breakdown of its fonts, colors, layout, typography, images, and design style.
</p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-md">
<a href="<%= user ? '/upload' : '/auth/register' %>" class="cta-glow bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container font-bold px-xl py-md rounded-xl hover:opacity-90 transition-all active:scale-95 flex items-center gap-xs text-body-lg">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">upload_file</span> Upload a Design
</a>
<a href="#process" class="border border-white/15 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md text-on-surface font-bold px-xl py-md rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all active:scale-95 text-body-lg flex items-center gap-xs">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">play_circle</span> Watch Demo
